132
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:13,279
And you know I think an exercise we often do is like what is wild success for X or what is wild success for Y and then equally what is terrible failure for those things and you can apply that

133
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:25,200
just to abstract thinking in different industries you can do that apply that for um we do that for the whole company for different areas of the company and I think just taking that very large long

