And so I think actually just making time to spend thinking about that is probably one of the most critical pieces.

159
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:25,120
Like just literally dreaming like what is wild success in 10 years?

160
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:27,440
What is terrible failure in 10 years?

161
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:38,640
um is a really great place to start is just like spending some time there and then like even if that is so big and so vast and so wild having that very first step is

